@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = v2
    tmp = wp.cos(v1)
    v2 = v2
    v2 = ((wp.abs(v2 + 0.06) / wp.exp(v0 + 0.29)) - (wp.exp(tmp + 0.40) + wp.sin(v1 + 0.54)))
    tmp = (v1 * wp.sin(wp.abs(v1 + 0.71)))
    v2 = 0.58
    v1 = (wp.exp((v2 + 0.51 / v2 + 0.31)) - (wp.exp(tmp + 0.52) * v2))
    data[tid] = v0
